title: S7E14 – "Existential Dread" – Scary Stories Told in the Dark
description:
In this episode of Scary Stories Told in the Dark, we bring you four spine-chilling tales from author Richard Saxon, performed by host and narrator Otis Jiry, about burdensome births, devilish diagnoses, unusual occupations, and oceanic abominations.
